            Flowp
    ~ More fun with Python ~


What is flowp ?

Flowp is a set of handy libraries / modules which should makes working 
with Python more enjoyable and productive.

For now flowp contains:

    - flowp.ftypes - better data structures / types processing
    - flowp.testing - better testing framework (BDD, influenced by RSpec)


Planned:

    - flowp.system - better files / process manipulation
    - flowp.build - (fluid) python building system
    - flowp.dsl - support for macros, very easy dsl (languages) creating
